<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Nolan Hill</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Nestled within the rolling hill slopes of northwest Calgary, Nolan Hill is a charming residential neighborhood that celebrates the old-world character of British Isles in an era gone by.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">With over 500 acres of idyllic landscapes, Nolan Hill is one of the most desirable communities in the city.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The immaculate greens and rustic stone details set against the backdrop of a breathtaking ravine system and natural ponds lend Nolan Hill real estate its distinctive quaint appeal.</p>
            <p class="par-xl">Also, the community offers a host of shopping and recreational venues such as playground, malls and elaborate parks for its residents.</p>
        </div>
